# Documentation Language

- Write repository documentation in French.
- Keep code identifiers, CLI commands, environment variables, routes, and package names unchanged.
- Prefer concise Markdown with working relative links.
- When source material is in English, translate the narrative prose but keep technical identifiers intact.
